      ],
      "source": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Saddle_Rock_Estates%2C_New_York"
    },
    {
      "id": 6,
      "text": "Because it is unincorporated, Saddle Rock Estates is governed directly by the Town of North Hempstead in Manhasset.",
